OL,3,C'Perpetrators will be held to
OL,4,Caccount': Probe launched into
OL,5,CPresbyterian church
OL,7,FPolice have launched a criminal
OL,8,Finvestigation into a safeguarding
OL,9,Fscandal within the Presbyterian Church
OL,10,Fof Ireland.
OL,12,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,13,FBeck said his investigation team aimed
OL,14,Fto make sure "perpetrators will be
OL,15,Fheld to account".
