OL,7,FHe also said the investigation would
OL,8,Fexamine if criminal offences had been
OL,9,Fcommitted by those responsible for
OL,10,Fsafeguarding in the PCI.
OL,12,FThe Church announced last week that
OL,13,Fmoderator Rev Trevor Gribben is to
OL,14,Fstand down after a review found
OL,15,F"serious and significant failings" in
OL,16,Fcentral safeguarding functions from
OL,17,Fthe period 2009 to 2022.
