OL,3,C'Perpetrators will be held to
OL,4,Caccount': Probe launched into
OL,5,CPresbyterian church
OL,7,FIt emerged that failures included
OL,8,Fsituations where the Church did not
OL,9,Frespond when people who had suffered
OL,10,Fharm sought help and instances where
OL,11,Foffenders returned to worship in
OL,12,Fchurch but were "inadequately
OL,13,Fmonitored".
OL,15,FThe PCI has welcomed the police probe
OL,16,Fand said it would be co-operating
OL,17,Ffully.
