OL,4,Caccount': Probe launched into
OL,5,CPresbyterian church
OL,7,FPolice confirmed last week that they
OL,8,Fwere involved in discussions with the
OL,9,FPCI after concerns were raised by the
OL,10,FChurch following the conviction of an
OL,11,Findividual in 2024 for child sexual
OL,12,Foffences.
OL,14,FSpeaking at a press conference in
OL,15,FBelfast on Monday, Mr Beck confirmed
OL,16,Fthe force was now looking at other
OL,17,Fpotential offenders.
OL,19,FHe confirmed that a "small number" of
OL,20,Fvictims had come forward.
