OL,7,FHe also said he had spoken with police
OL,8,Fin the Republic of Ireland as there
OL,9,Fwas the potential for it to be a cross-
OL,10,Fborder investigation.
OL,12,FHe said: "Over the last number of days
OL,13,Fwe have been working with statutory
OL,14,Fpartners to formalise a coordinated
OL,15,Fresponse to address the matters that
OL,16,Fhave come to light as a result of the
OL,17,Frecent announcement by the
OL,18,FPresbyterian Church in Ireland.
