OL,7,F"My immediate priority and that of the
OL,8,FPSNI is the protection and the
OL,9,Fsafeguarding of anyone who may have
OL,10,Fbeen affected.
OL,12,F"In that regard I have established a
OL,13,Fdedicated PSNI investigation team
OL,14,Funder the supervision of an
OL,15,Fexperienced senior investigating
OL,16,Fofficer from our public protection
OL,17,Fbranch.
OL,19,F"This officer will lead what I can
OL,20,Fconfirm today will be a criminal
OL,21,Finvestigation."
