OL,7,FMr Beck added: "The role of the PSNI
OL,8,Fwill be to investigate all criminal
OL,9,Foffences and to work closely with
OL,10,Fstatutory partners under the joint
OL,11,Fprotocol arrangements.
OL,13,F"That is to ensure victims can access
OL,14,Fthe criminal justice process and
OL,15,Fperpetrators will be held to account.
