OL,5,CPresbyterian church
OL,7,F"We would encourage anyone who is
OL,8,Fsuffering or who is affected to speak
OL,9,Fwith our dedicated investigative team
OL,10,Fwho will be on hand to provide
OL,11,Fspecialist advice and signposting to
OL,12,Fother key services.
OL,14,F"If I can speak directly to victims, I
OL,15,Frecognise that this may be difficult
OL,16,Fand you may not be ready. That is OK.
OL,17,FWe want to hear from you, you will be
OL,18,Ftreated with sensitivity, with respect
OL,19,Fand with professionalism.
