OL,7,FA spokesperson for the PCI said,
OL,8,F"Having been informed by the Police
OL,9,FService of Northern Ireland that they
OL,10,Fhave launched a criminal investigation
OL,11,Fwe welcome this believing it will
OL,12,Fprovide a thorough, trusted and
OL,13,Ftransparent outcome. We will co-
OL,14,Foperate fully with the investigation.
OL,16,F"We will make available all relevant
OL,17,Ffiles, reports and information to
OL,18,Fassist police with their inquiries.
